<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٣٩٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1547">حَفْصُ بْنُ عُمَرَ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6685">هِشَامٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«ضَحَّى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِكَبْشَيْنِ، يُسَمِّي وَيُكَبِّرُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>